data.description: Welcome to this breathtaking 2019-built home, a masterpiece of comfort and modern living. Sprawled across a generous floor plan, this house boasts an impressive array of six bedrooms and five full bathrooms, including the convenience of a main level bedroom and bathroom.  Step inside to discover a beautifully maintained interior, where a cozy fireplace sets a warm, inviting ambiance in the spacious living area. Each bedroom is a retreat of its own, offering generous dimensions for rest and rejuvenation.  Entertainment and family life find their perfect setting here, with a large, open loft area upstairs. Whether it's a game night, a dedicated homeschooling space, or an expansive home office, this loft adapts to your lifestyle needs.  The kitchen, truly the heart of this home, is a culinary dream. It features a large island that not only adds to the functionality but also serves as a social hub for gatherings.  Additional luxuries include a fully finished walkout basement, leading to a beautifully fenced yard equipped with a sprinkler system for an evergreen lawn. The substantial driveway can easily accommodate multiple vehicles, enhancing the practicality of this home.  Location is paramount, and this home sits just 5 miles from I-95, in close proximity to a commuter lot and public transportation, perfect for commuters and travelers.  Merging modern amenities with a spacious design and prime location, this property is a rare gem. Seize the chance to make this haven of comfort and luxury your new home. Don't delay, as opportunities like this are few and far between!
